1. Goal of This Workflow

To ensure that:

Every daily journal is persistently saved

All segmentation files are updated deterministically

GitHub becomes the authoritative memory

Claude can later read history and answer questions

2. System Roles
Claude

Reasoning and segmentation engine

Reads and writes files logically

Decides what goes where based on definitions

GitHub

Permanent storage

